## ğŸš€ Quick Deploy Checklist

### Local Setup (5 minutes)
```bash
1. Clone repo
2. npm install
3. Copy .env.example to .env
4. Add Telegram credentials
5. npm start
6. Visit localhost:3000
```

### Render Deploy (10 minutes)
```bash
1. Push to GitHub
2. Connect to Render
3. Add environment variables
4. Deploy!
5. Live at your-app.onrender.com
```

### Post-Deploy (15 minutes)
```bash
1. Test all features
2. Add Adsterra codes
3. Submit to Google Search Console
4. Setup UptimeRobot
5. Share on social media
```

